          "text": {
            "content": "Gareth meets me at Mdumbi backpackers and we have a chat about horse poo. Siya is volunteering here. I meet Isipileh and his broken bicycle, we fix it together. He helped me find a campsite and then he cycled along with me on my run down to the beach. \n",
            "link": null
